": 1671266422, "deleted": 0, "content": "在校学生，软件工程方向，趁着发了奖学金换了台电脑，但是看网上都说 32G 起步，搞得我有点内存焦虑了，我想知道学生平时就开开 idea ，pycharm 等 jetbrain 全家桶还有虚拟机之类的，16G RAM 够不够用", "content_rendered": "<p>在校学生，软件工程方向，趁着发了奖学金换了台电脑，但是看网上都说 32G 起步，搞得我有点内存焦虑了，我想知道学生平时就开开 idea ，pycharm 等 jetbrain 全家桶还有虚拟机之类的，16G RAM 够不够用</p>\n", "last_modified": 1671266422, "replies": 46, "id": 903157}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 194656, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3652, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 390543, "username": "devfeng", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/devfeng", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23d1/9b45/390543_mini.png?m=1671274594", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23d1/9b45/390543_normal.png?m=1671274594", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23d1/9b45/390543_large.png?m=1671274594", "created": 1552029856, "last_modified": 1671274594}, "last_reply_by": "Kiriya", "last_touched": 1671328298, "title": "上个月搬到新租的公寓，今天收到中央空调电费账单 1200 元，这个合理吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/903179", "created": 1671275003, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近一直居家办公，空调开的比较多，有时候晚上睡觉也忘记关，电费商业用电是 1.3 元。问了管家说是空调 25 匹，一直开着电费就是这个价，感觉被骗了，有老哥帮忙看看吗？\r\n![图片]( https://imgur.com/wxMSKfQ)", "content_rendered": "<p>最近一直居家办公，空调开的比较多，有时候晚上睡觉也忘记关，电费商业用电是 1.3 元。问了管家说是空调 25 匹，一直开着电费就是这个价，感觉被骗了，有老哥帮忙看看吗？\n<img alt=\"图片\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://imgur.com/wxMSKfQ\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1671275200, "replies": 36, "id": 903179}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 194656, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3652, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 383741, "username": "jingcoco", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jingcoco", "website": "", "twitter": "jingzhengyi", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/deeb/96cc/383741_mini.png?m=1612325504", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/deeb/96cc/383741_normal.png?m=1612325504", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/deeb/96cc/383741_large.png?m=1612325504", "created": 1550114725, "last_modified": 1612325504}, "last_reply_by": "Badlink", "last_touched": 1671304857, "title": "小白从宫崎英高产生的疑惑,游戏制作最重要的不是程序员是游戏制作人吗?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/903169", "created": 1671271854, "deleted": 0, "content": "看游戏玩家老是说宫崎英高是神,小岛秀夫是神....然后查了一下,\r\n\r\n- 宫崎英高 是游戏制作人.\r\n\r\n- 然后查了一下游戏制作人工作, 开发总监和 创意总监\r\n\r\n- 我是知道 PM 之类的项目经理压力大,来自大领导之类的客户之类的压力.但是意思是说如果一家公司有很多钱 就能出很好的作品吗,感觉这个肯定不成立.\r\n\r\n小白....", "content_rendered": "<p>看游戏玩家老是说宫崎英高是神,小岛秀夫是神....然后查了一下,</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>宫崎英高 是游戏制作人.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>然后查了一下游戏制作人工作, 开发总监和 创意总监</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>我是知道 PM 之类的项目经理压力大,来自大领导之类的客户之类的压力.但是意思是说如果一家公司有很多钱 就能出很好的作品吗,感觉这个肯定不成立.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>小白....</p>\n", "last_modified": 1671271854, "replies": 29, "id": 903169}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 194656, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3652, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 73974, "username": "seers", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/seers", "website": "hushi.me", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/46ae/84c9/73974_mini.png?m=1654183948", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/46ae/84c9/73974_normal.png?m=1654183948", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/46ae/84c9/73974_large.png?m=1654183948", "created": 1410770596, "last_modified": 1654183948}, "last_reply_by": "BaseException", "last_touched": 1671328948, "title": "有没有 1k 到 1k5 左右好玩的电子产品", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/903173", "created": 1671272276, "deleted": 0, "content": "今年活干得好，领导说年底奖励一个礼物，1k-1k5 左右，不能是钱只能是东西，想了想都不知道买啥好，来头脑风暴一下，AirPods 已有，其他苹果全家桶这个价格也买不到，机械键盘也有，狗屁王也有。", "content_rendered": "<p>今年活干得好，领导说年底奖励一个礼物，1k-1k5 左右，不能是钱只能是东西，想了想都不知道买啥好，来头脑风暴一下，AirPods 已有，其他苹果全家桶这个价格也买不到，机械键盘也有，狗屁王也有。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1671272276, "replies": 28, "id": 903173}]